title: Snap worldwide net income 2015 to 2019
yAxis: Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars, containing a total of 5 data points.
In general Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars has rose over the Year.
Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars is roughly constant from 2015 to 2016, gradually increasing from 2016 to 2017, and finally roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars, of value 3445.07 was reached at Year 2017
Minimum Income/ loss in million U.S. dollars about 372.89 was reached at Year 2015
